com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters

Class PrivateDataCallListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.CallListenerAdapter
      • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.PrivateDataCallListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, CallListener, PrivateDataCallListener

    public class PrivateDataCallListenerAdapter
extends CallListenerAdapter
implements PrivateDataCallListener
    An adapter which is notified of receipt of platform specific call information. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
